Q: ACI Jet在2024年每个月的飞行量及其环比增长或下降百分比。
SQL:
WITH biao_1 AS (
        SELECT
                a.date_month,
                b.supplier_id,
                COUNT(*) AS num
        FROM
                zts_plane_flight_1 a
                JOIN aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
        WHERE
                b.supplier_id = "1019"
                AND a.date_month BETWEEN '2024-01'
                AND '2024-12'
        GROUP BY
                a.date_month,
                b.supplier_id
        ),
        biao_2 AS ( SELECT *, LAG( num ) OVER ( PARTITION BY supplier_id ORDER BY date_month ) AS last_num FROM biao_1 ) SELECT
        date_month,
        supplier_id,
        num,
        last_num,
        concat( ROUND((( num - last_num ) / last_num ) * 100, 2 ), '%' ) AS rate
FROM
        biao_2
ORDER BY
        date_month ASC;
actual_SQL:
WITH monthly_flights AS (
    SELECT
        a.date_month,
        COUNT(*) AS flight_count
    FROM
        zts_plane_flight_1 a
        JOIN aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
    WHERE
        b.supplier_id = "1019"
        AND a.date_month BETWEEN '2024-01' AND '2024-12'
    GROUP BY
        a.date_month
),
monthly_growth AS (
    SELECT
        date_month,
        flight_count,
        LAG(flight_count) OVER (ORDER BY date_month) AS previous_month_count
    FROM
        monthly_flights
)
SELECT
    date_month,
    flight_count,
    previous_month_count,
    CONCAT(ROUND(((flight_count - previous_month_count) / previous_month_count) * 100, 2), '%') AS growth_rate
FROM
    monthly_growth
ORDER BY
    date_month ASC;
